    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1891-03-09T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1891-03-09T00:00:00-05:00" n="400" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d400">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Pung</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Blaine</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Chinese
                                        Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1891-03-09">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 9,
                                1891</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to bring to your kind
                            notice the gratifying announcement of the following cablegram from the
                            foreign office in Peking, received yesterday: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>All the ministers had an audience on the 25th day of the present
                                    month (March 5th, instant), and were banqueted on the following
                                    day (March 6, instant). Appropriate ceremonies were most
                                    pleasantly observed on both occasions. Please communicate the
                                    above to the honorable Secretary of State of the United
                                    States.</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <p>Accept, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Pung Kwang Yu</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
